  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT251-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">piriviṭait tōḻi “paruvam aṉṟu paṭṭatu vampu” eṉṟu vaṟpuṟuttiyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">The confidante encouraging [with the words] “that isn't
          the season; it has happened out of time”, in the time of separation. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT251">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>maṭava vāḻi maññai yāyiṉaṅ</l>
          <l>kāla māri peyteṉa vataṉeti</l>
          <l>rālalu māliṉa piṭavum pūttaṉa</l>
          <l>kāraṉ ṟikuḷai tīrkaniṉ paṭarē</l>
          <l>kaḻinta mārik koḻinta paḻanīr</l>
          <l>putunīr koḷīiya vukuttaru</l>
          <l>notumal vāṉattu muḻaṅkukural kēṭṭē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>Ignorant they [are], oh [friend] , the peacocks in choice groups,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">hearing the thundering voice of the indifferent sky</l>
          <l rend="indent4">which sheds, in order to take in new water,</l>
          <l rend="indent4">the old water that stayed behind from passed showers.</l>
          <l rend="indent2">In the face of that, because a timely shower has rained, </l>
          <l>they have danced [their] dance</l>
          <l rend="indent8">and the Piṭavu plants have begun to flower.</l>
          <l>It is not the rainy season, friend, may your affliction end.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
